    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/f0359bc3428b639c2c43515b7ddced7f.poster.avif?t=1770374168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/f0359bc3428b639c2c43515b7ddced7f.webm?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/f0359bc3428b639c2c43515b7ddced7f.mp4?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The Evil DLC </strong> 扩展了使Little Big Workshop卓越的原因！你的工厂一周周扭亏为盈，但你仍然感到不满足？那是时候把企业贪婪的转盘转向邪恶！这不只是一种新外观。产品、公司、破坏活动、技能和恶意技巧将在竞争中胜出，还有更多。The Evil DLC将光荣的工厂变成邪恶的仙境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/fdb247a4c87930423e9861e92d714a78.poster.avif?t=1770374168\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/fdb247a4c87930423e9861e92d714a78.webm?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/fdb247a4c87930423e9861e92d714a78.mp4?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>加入阴暗面</strong></h2>作为臭名昭著的布拉德（来自原始游戏中的卡通风格超级恶棍）的学徒，创办一个新工厂，并学习如何经营一个不遵守规则的成功工厂！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>邪恶的计划和新技能</strong></h2>此DLC包含了一个全新的技术树，里面充满了肮脏的把戏和厚脸皮的升级。你的工人在工作中偷懒？雇用一位残酷的霸主，将他们的动机恢复原状。竞争对手在自由市场上击败你？派出间谍以找出他们的弱点并狠狠地利用它们。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与新公司竞争</strong></h2>当然，你可以公平地击败你的竞争者……或者只是继续破坏你周围的每个人以获得优势，最终你将可以挑战布拉德本人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超过30种新产品。</strong></h2>.包括VR耳机，拥有的花园侏儒，外星人模具（讨厌!）、弯曲的踏板车、大蒜枪和复古风格的机器人。<br><br><i>对于寻求新挑战的熟练玩家，建议使用DLC，我们建议您在尝试扩展之前先玩基础游戏。</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2>- 焕然一新的进度系统，让你与其他公司竞争<br>- 超过30种新产品，以及一系列全新的工作站、装饰等<br>- 新鲜的技能树，让你释放黑暗面的真正力量<br>- 破坏系统给你不公平的市场优势<br>- 工人的恐怖服装<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/81da6fc748c506f28cd732957a37c333.poster.avif?t=1770374168\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/81da6fc748c506f28cd732957a37c333.webm?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1426880/extras/81da6fc748c506f28cd732957a37c333.mp4?t=1770374168\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
